<c74object name='dk.corpuslist' category='' module='dataknot'>
    <digest>Visualize the sample contents of a corpus
</digest>
    <description>The <o>dk.corpuslist</o> object loads and displays the contents of the <o>polybuffer~</o> or <o>buffer~</o> at the center of a corpus, allowing the viewing of the selected samples.
</description>
    <discussion>If you want to learn more about the underlying algorithms have a look at these articles:<br/><a href="https://learn.flucoma.org/reference/kdtree">https://learn.flucoma.org/reference/kdtree</a><br/><a href="https://learn.flucoma.org/reference/mlpregressor">https://learn.flucoma.org/reference/mlpregressor</a>
</discussion>

